{"tid":868114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無私隱架喇！發現轉數快有bug！","createTime":"2018-10-19T08:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T10:48:56.000Z","uid":130894,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d462487c9accb77db61f75bbdf8a392afba3ca3","tid":868114,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"無啦啦收到2個唔識既人過$0.01俾我<br />\n本身有啲驚，但諗諗下，其實轉數快只要入個電話就可以大概估到你個名，就算估唔到，都一定知個姓，咁咪好易起到人底？<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n1. 網上識左個異性，佢想陰你俾假名你，你一野就可以拆穿到佢西洋鏡，可以試一試佢個莊。<br />\n2. Cold call撚可以好輕鬆就知你姓乜，入一入個電話就知你係乜先生乜小姐。<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他大家諗到既神奇用法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee3f6e929a9a0b5672a16cdb9a869aa5a757e74","tid":868114,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"mo啦mo啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次玩撚完喇！"},{"pid":"c18b3ce56e340c90bfac87f79f04e7607894f198","tid":868114,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮！岀黎隻揪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪你過一仙俾我咁柒孤寒？！"},{"pid":"1edbdf0b1f5b8c2ca6a750cfd673dbb9311c06fa","tid":868114,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"有錢收仲咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5643fd04c59ab812e61d29eaee82e1bccb690834","tid":868114,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"點解無人同我討論下？我覺得呢個係一個天大既發現！<b